PLANTS OF SOUTH CAROLINA
Pickens County

*Galax aphylla* L.

Sassafras Mountain. From the town of Rocky
Bottom, travel north on SC-199 about two miles
(follow road to end) to look out tower. The seep
area is just below the tower at an elevation of
3600 ft. 35.0635N and 87.7707W.
